  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 390°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Peel and finely dice <strong>half </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>red onion</strong> reserving the rest for later</p>\n<p>Dice 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching <span class=\"text-highlight\">lid),</span> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped red onion</strong>,<strong> tomato</strong> and <strong>garlic </strong>to the pan and cook for 5 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the<strong> lamb mince</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>ground allspice</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong></p>\n<p>Cook for 10-12 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go, until the lamb is cooked through and is starting to crisp – this is your <strong>spiced lamb</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, add the <strong>plain naans</strong> to a baking tray</p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 8-10 min or until the naans are crispy</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2408Step-4-x400.jpg",
