          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and slice the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>remaining</strong></span><strong> red onion</strong> (as finely as you can!)</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>remaining tomato</strong> roughly </p>",
